name: SEEK YOU
description: I promise this is the last reductive syntax word crystal for awhile. Sometimes I just get carried away with the concepts of something that my mind can't stop figuring them out or seeing them. I used to fight it, now I just let it go and see where my mind lands. I've never been tested or diagnosed with Asperger's or being on the autism spectrum, but good god if this book isn't proof then I don't know what is. Again...I digress. In SEEK YOU we can reduce or minimize the letter usage to attain ultimate simplification: CQ. There are plenty of these sub-genre gems out there. We've only scratched the surface!
